<DOC><DOCNO> ZF32-026-115 </DOCNO><DOCID>11 452 218</DOCID><JOURNAL>MacWEEK  Oct 29 1991 v5 n37 p6(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Coastal Associates Publishing L.P. 1991.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Paragon caters to PowerBook buyers with slimmed-down NisusCompact. (Paragon Concepts Inc.'s Nisus Compact word processor forApple's PowerBooks) (product announcement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Said, Carolyn.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Paragon Concepts Inc. (Product introduction).andO;Product:   Nisus Compact (Word processing software) (Product introduction)Apple Macintosh PowerBook (Portable computer) (Computer programs).andO;Topic:     Product IntroductionWord Processing SoftwareNotebook ComputersEnhancements.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>By Carolyn SaidandM;Las Vegas -- Those lightweight Mac PowerBooks will need similarly trimsoftware, and Paragon Concepts Inc. is eager to oblige.andP;  The companyannounced last week Nisus Compact, a new version of its Nisus word processordesigned especially for the PowerBooks.andM;Priced at $150, compared with Nisus' $395 price tag, Nisus Compact retainsmost of the full-fledged version's word processing capabilities but has fewergraphics and page-layout features, Paragon said.andM;Nisus Compact, due to ship this year, will address the special needs ofPowerBook users in several ways, Paragon said.andP;  The program minimizes itsaccess of the hard disk to conserve battery power.andP;  It will run on less than300 Kbytes of RAM, compared with the 1 Mbyte recommended for Nisus, andweighs in at about 350 Kbytes vs.andP;  800 Kbytes forNisus Compact willincorporate a new way to help keep files organized and accessible.andP;  Whenusers create a file, they can check off several categories to which itbelongs, which will simplify finding the file at a later date.andM;The program also incorporates a new &quot;fuzzy&quot; text-search feature that willallow users to find items with only partial details.andM;Nisus Compact files will be cross-compatible with Nisus 3.06 files.andP;  As inNisus, the compact version will use a file format that allows any otherapplication to read the text portion of files.andM;Paragon Concepts Inc. is at 990 Highland Drive, Suite 312, Solana Beach,Calif.andP;  92075.andP;  Phone (619) 481-1477; fax (619) 481-6154.andO;</TEXT></DOC>